<plot>The music of Rachmaninov accompanies a solitary man who walks through a cold and forbidding urban landscape during a stormy night. Under his arm he carries a film; he's a projectionist. As he passes walls and windows, scenes from movies appear. Dawn comes at last.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?584445</url></doc>
